                    <u><b>IMPORTANT NOTE:</b></u> Your shipment will be insured on your instructions by Grace Relocations.
                    Your shipment is to be valued for insurance purposes at replacement value. This is important. Also all items
                    valued at over Rs 10,000.00 must be separately indicated as these as per insurance requirements qualify for
                    special protective packing.</div>     
                <p>
                    Insurance Company does not entertain any claims on the packages, which are packed by owner.
                </p>    
                <p>
                    Also in the event of damage or loss please note the following:
                    
                </p> 
                <div style="text-align:justify">903194192.  Check all items as well the individual contents against the inventory list at the time of delivery into the 
                    residence.</div>     
                <div style="text-align:justify">903194193.  Ask the crew to assist in locating any items that appear to be missing.  Because there is a 
                    large amount of packing material, it is possible that certain items could get misplaced amongst the discarded
                    paper.</div>  
                <div style="text-align:justify">903194194.  Items or any contents definitely not received or damaged are to be recorded as missing / 
                    damaged on the inventory sheet as well as on the destination delivery document / with a verifying signature 
                    by the delivery supervisor.</div>      
                
                <div style="text-align:justify">903194112. Note any damage in detail on the inventory sheet (for e.g. dresser, right leg broken or spoon
                    (set of six) one missing, etc.</div>      
                
                <div style="text-align:justify">903193872. Do not dispose or attempt to repair any of the items that you may want to recover an 
                    insurance compensation.</div>          
                
                <div style="text-align:justify">903193792. Notify the damage to the Grace Relocations destination branch office or the origin office immediately 
                    in writing and enclosing therein the following: -                
                    <ul>
                        <li>List of items damaged or missing as well as delivery supervisors verification report.</li>
                        <li>Package number as per Grace Relocations Inventory.</li>
                        <li>Description of damage and insured value</li>
                        <li>Repair / replacement cost.</li>
                        <li>Amount of compensation you are seeking for each individual item.</li>
                    </ul>            
                    
                </div>     
